Biggart, Respondent, v. Manhattan El. R. Co. et al., Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 14, 1890.) Appeal from special term.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Davies & Rapallo, for appellant. J. A. Weekes, Jr., for respondents.

No opinion. Order reversed, with costs.
